ansition-colors\">Immortaliser son Couple</a><a href=\"https://haroboz.com/votre-experience/premier-shooting-nu/\" class=\"block px-6 py-3 text-sm hover:bg-brand-50 hover:text-brand transition-colors\">Cadeau &amp; Célébration</a></div></div></div>\n                    <div class=\"mega-menu-item relative h-full flex items-center\"><button class=\"flex items-center text-sm font-medium hover:text-brand-light transition-colors py-8\">Où me trouver ? <i data-lucide=\"chevron-down\" class=\"ml-1 w-4 h-4\"></i></button><div class=\"mega-menu-content absolute top-20 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 w-48 bg-white shadow-xl rounded-b-lg border-t border-gray-100\"><div class=\"py-2\"><a href=\"https://haroboz.com/photographe/photographe-marseille/\" class=\"block px-6 py-3 text-sm hover:bg-brand-50 hover:text-brand transition-colors\">Marseille</a><a href=\"https://haroboz.com/photographe/photographe-toulon/\" class=\"block px-6 py-3 text-sm hover:bg-brand-50 hover:text-brand transition-colors\">Toulon</a><a href=\"https://haroboz.com/photographe/photographe-nice/\" class=\"block px-6 py-3 text-sm hover:bg-brand-50 hover:text-brand transition-colors\">Nice</a><a href=\"https://haroboz.com/photographe/photographe-paris/\" class=\"block px-6 py-3 text-sm hover:bg-brand-50 hover:text-brand transition-colors\">Paris</a></div></div></div>\n                    <div class=\"mega-menu-item relative h-full flex items-center\"><button class=\"flex items-center text-sm font-medium hover:text-brand-light transition-colors py-8\">L'Oeuvre <i data-lucide=\"chevron-down\" class=\"ml-1 w-4 h-4\"></i></button><div class=\"mega-menu-content absolute top-20 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 w-64 bg-white shadow-xl rounded-b-lg border-t border-gray-100 overflow-hidden\"><div class=\"py-2\"><a href=\"https://haroboz.com/portfolio/\" class=\"block px-6 py-3 text-sm hover:bg-brand-50 hover:text-brand transition-colors\">Toutes les oeuvres</a><a href=\"https://haroboz.com/portfolio/galerie-portraits-hommes/\" cla